==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: E-la
<hw>E"-la`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Originally, the highest
note in the scale of Guido; hence, proverbially, any extravagant
saying.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Why, this is above <xex>E-la</xex>!⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Beau. & Fl.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>El Aaiun</ent>⟦br⟧
